of the oil fields, she disclosed, noting that Angola has a bright
future in its oil industry.
</P>
<P>
Assis said the development of the oil industry in the country
would be beneficial to the region, as Angola would be able to
supply its neighbors with oil and petroleum products when the
construction of new oil refineries, including one in the coastal
city of Lobito, is completed.
</P>
<P>
Angola would pay more attention to training its own
technicians with the construction of some new refineries, Assis
promised. 
