off-loading of shares continued.
</P>
<P>
The KSE 100 Index dropped 9 points to close at 765.74 against
the previous trading day's close of 774.74 points.
</P>
<P>
There were 18 gainers and 43 losers while share prices of 35
companies remained unchanged.
</P>
