<HEADLINE> New Zealand Stocks Finish Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WELLINGTON, July 14 (Xinhua) -- The New Zealand sharemarket
closed higher on Tuesday after a day of quiet and good trading.
</P>
