pierced through the sky of Paris at the beginning of the ceremony.
</P>
<P>
This year's parade reflected the on-going professionalization
and reform engaged by the French armed forces since 1996,
emphasizing closer collaboration among army, navy, air force and
police in future military operations.
</P>
<P>
The cadets of prestigious military schools such as
Polytechnique and Saint-Cyr also joined the parade as
usual. 
