<HEADLINE> Senior CPC Official Meets With PCP Delegation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 14 (Xinhua) -- Ding Guangen, member of the
Political Bureau of the Communist Party of China (CPC) Central
Committee, met with a delegation from the Portuguese Communist
Party (PCP) here today.
</P>
<P>
