is an inseparable part of Serbia.
</P>
<P>
The Kosovo issue was related to the national security of
Yugoslavia and had to be solved through democratic means, he said.
</P>
<P>
On July 13, 1941, the people of Montenegro, under the
leadership of the Yugoslav Communist party, launched a large-scale
armed uprising. The struggle was finally won four years later at
the end of the war. 
