The new contract is part of Exxon's long-term commitment to
cooperate with Chinese petroleum and petrochemical firms.
</P>
<P>
With more than 30 years of research and development experience,
Jinzhou Petrochemical Co. is one of China's largest makers of
lubricant additives.
</P>
<P>
Exxon Chemical Co, a division of Exxon Corp, is a major global
producer and supplier of a wide range of petrochemicals.  
